name: quickdraw
description: A theme for atom that is quick and simple to configure
readme:
# quickdraw Syntax Theme for Atom 1.0

A quickdraw theme for Atom that adheres to the vim theme. Easy on the eyes, beautiful theme.

A big thanks to Isaac Hess for creating the [original quickdraw theme for Atom](https://github.com/isaachess/quickdraw-atom) on which this is based.

Based on [https://github.com/morhetz/quickdraw](https://github.com/morhetz/quickdraw).

![Screenshot](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/caleb/quickdraw-syntax-atom/master/quickdraw.png)
